title: 'Fix PSM pallet storage version to allow V1 migration on fresh deployment'
doc:
- audience: Runtime Dev
  description: |-
    Fixes the PSM pallet's in-code storage version from 1 to 0 so that the V1
    migration runs on first deployment. Previously, `BeforeAllRuntimeMigrations`
    initialized the on-chain version to 1 (matching the in-code version), causing
    `MigrateToV1` to be silently skipped.

crates:
- name: pallet-psm
  bump: patch
